lead_paragraph: Former New Zealand captain DJ Forbes is hoping some of the winning culture he helped establish will be transferred to a new generation as he prepares to break the Sevens World Series appearances record in Dubai this week.

headline.print_headline: Sevens Record Breaker Forbes Aims to Set Standard for Generation Next
